 bed. Made it right after work. My oven naturally runs 50 degrees too hot so I turned it down. The crust was getting a bit dark so I took it out. The crust is GREAT. The inside is just slightly undercooked (still very good) so next time I&#8217;ll turn the temp down by 25 degrees and cook longer since mine only took 15 minutes. Can&#8217;t wait to try some salad sandwiches :D</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/12/no-knead-ciabatta/?replytocom=66360#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-66360\", \"66360\", \"respond\", \"13392\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-66391\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/10447062948233821387' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jessica</a></cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2010/12/no-knead-ciabatta/#comment-66391\">06.16.12 at 5:45 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>I made this last night/today with multigrain bread flour. It turned out a bit dense because of the multigrain flour, but it&#8217;s full of flax and other goodness so we are devouring it happily anyways. Makes amazing sandwiches!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/12/no-knead-ciabatta/?replytocom=66391#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-66391\", \"66391\", \"respond\", \"13392\")'>Re